&gt;&gt;Julie: I'm Julie Westcurkin from The Author's
Team in Santa Monica. Today we are very excited

00:00:09.650 --> 00:00:14.490
to welcome The Beer Chicks: Christina Perozzi,
and Hallie Beaune.

