and to talk about their book, "The Naked Pint:

00:00:22.770 --> 00:00:28.810
An Unadulterated Guide to Craft Beer". Christina
was named "Best Beer Sommelier" in Los Angeles

00:00:28.810 --> 00:00:31.279
by Los Angeles Times Magazine in 2008.

00:00:31.279 --> 00:00:34.190
[audience cheers and applauds]

00:00:34.190 --> 00:00:39.410
She managed The Original Father's Office here
in Santa Monica, which I think a few of you

00:00:39.410 --> 00:00:40.789
have been to.

00:00:40.789 --> 00:00:41.789
[clapping]

00:00:41.789 --> 00:00:45.219
