everywhere, she founded the popular website:

00:00:45.219 --> 00:00:50.230
beerforchicks.com and started working as a
consultant, a beer educator, a writer, and

00:00:50.230 --> 00:00:56.339
beer sommelier in 2006. And Hallie is also
a beer sommelier and the resident beer expert

00:00:56.339 --> 00:01:01.899
on the hit cable foodie show After Hours with
Daniel Boulud. She met Christina working at

00:01:01.899 --> 00:01:06.560
Father's Office and started the popular FO
Beer School there. So, please join me in welcoming

00:01:06.560 --> 00:01:08.420
Hallie and Christina.

00:01:08.420 --> 00:01:09.420
[clapping]

