at work and now I see that it has changed
in a couple of years.

00:01:18.650 --> 00:01:20.370
&gt;&gt;Hallie: Thank God.

00:01:20.370 --> 00:01:21.370
[laughing]

00:01:21.370 --> 00:01:24.660
&gt;&gt;Christina: Anyway, thank you so much for
coming; and thank you so much for having us.

00:01:24.660 --> 00:01:29.170
Um, when we started this beer journey, we
never ever imagined in a million years that

00:01:29.170 --> 00:01:35.040
we would be standing some place like this
talking about beer, or talking about our book.

00:01:35.040 --> 00:01:39.000
But, um, we decided that the best way to talk
about our book since the book is about beer

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:41.480
is just to talk about beer and you can read
the book later.

00:01:41.480 --> 00:01:42.480
[laugh]

00:01:42.480 --> 00:01:43.480
&gt;&gt;Hallie: And drink it

