&gt;&gt;Hallie: um, it is just about about high
school? Anyone? No.

00:06:53.270 --> 00:06:54.270
[laughter]

00:06:54.270 --> 00:06:57.210
&gt;&gt;Hallie: Um, you know just drink it just
