00:06:57.210 --> 00:07:01.060
comes in a nice glass, it's supposed to come
in a nice glass because you want to get all

00:07:01.060 --> 00:07:04.500
the flavors, you wanna get all the aromatics
in there.

00:07:04.500 --> 00:07:08.310
&gt;&gt;Christina: Um, and also you know with wine
when you're when people are evaluating wine

00:07:08.310 --> 00:07:13.719
they already have, there is a certain set
of descriptors that are already defined. You

00:07:13.719 --> 00:07:19.930
know there's a wheel that tobacco and spice
and you know fruity and dark cherries; but

00:07:19.930 --> 00:07:25.650
in beer there isn't that yet. It, it can be
